    Input Text    ${PIPELINE_DESC_INPUT_XP}    ${name}
    Run Keyword And Continue On Failure
    ...    Element Should Be Disabled    ${GENERIC_CREATE_BTN_XP}
    Select Pipeline For The Run    pipeline_name=${pipeline_name}
